### 1. CopyHandler Method (Full Implementation)
**Location:** `/private/var/folders/vq/9q38rw0x2455zr_whqcrjbhr0000gn/T/planmode-bench-wt-run-1775386144747-hzhhg8/server/routes.go:1446-1483`

